 <span data-ttu-id="2085b-237">Aby uzyskać więcej informacji, zobacz <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> i <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Addition%2A> operatorów.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2085b-237">For more information, see the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Addition%2A> operators.</span></span>  
  
